peer.c is an independent UDP peer derived solely from tests/bad_dtls_test.c in
OpenConnect commit 2035601b64a5360a46d18e08937e7f654b3230f2. It preserves the
Cisco DTLS1_BAD_VER 0x0100 wire contract, body-only handshake transcript,
TLS 1.0 PRF, AES128-SHA record construction, and HelloVerify cookie exchange.
